OL,3,CProposition lodged to improve funding
OL,4,Cfor IVF treatment
OL,6,FIf these changes are approved, would
OL,7,Ffall in line with UK and Europe
OL,8,Fguidelines.
OL,10,FIn the current means-tested system,
OL,11,Fthere is funding for the full cost of
OL,12,Ftreatment for couples with a combined
OL,13,Fincome of up to #40,795.
OL,15,FHowever, if two people work full-time
OL,16,Fon minimum wage, they would have a
OL,17,Fcombined salary above that.
OL,19,FDeputy Stephenson says no one has ever
OL,20,Fqualified for the full funding as it
OL,21,Fis so restrictive.
