OL,6,FShe added: "Providing fair funding
OL,7,Fkeeps today's workers here, I know
OL,8,Flack of funding has driven some away."
OL,10,FFertility charity Tiny Seeds has been
OL,11,Fcampaigning for a change in policy for
OL,12,Fyears and welcomes the proposition.
