OL,3,CProposition lodged to improve funding
OL,4,Cfor IVF treatment
OL,6,FOperations Manager Chloe Fosse said:
OL,7,F"Infertility is a disease and it is
OL,8,Ftime that our government and
OL,9,Fhealthcare system recognise it as
OL,10,Fsuch. The current means-tested funding
OL,11,Fsystem is outdated and unobtainable to
OL,12,Falmost all and as a charity, we have
OL,13,Fvoiced over and over again the real-
OL,14,Flife impact that the lack of a fair
OL,15,Fand equitable funding system is having
OL,16,Fon those who need IVF treatment to
OL,17,Fconceive."
OL,19,FMinisters are expected to discuss the
OL,20,Fproposition later this week.
